      propertyPath: m_value.<Name>k__BackingField
      value: '[hopeful] Though the battles are fierce, I be'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8045659150639517358, guid: fbcc40e91526859428bab09db558e208, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_value.<Text>k__BackingField
      value: "[hopeful] Though the battles are fierce, I believe the era of the medieval
        warrior is far from over. [inspired] With each challenge, I grow stronger,
        wiser, and more resilient. [optimistic] The stories I carry will inspire
        others to stand brave against any foe. [reflective] For in this age of knights
        and legends, a true warrior never gives up \u2014 he fights on, no matter
        the odds."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
